  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors addressed; one factor (Numerical solver error) carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' on the basis that the commercial solver's internal convergence routines are considered transparent to the analyst team and therefore outside the scope of the credibility assessment — an argument that does not satisfy the 'not-applicable' criterion but has not been formally substantiated.",
